item.title: CVE-2019-1010287|2024-08-05T03:07:18.471Z -- timesheet%20next%20gen -- timesheet%20next%20gen
item.description: Timesheet Next Gen 1.5.3 and earlier is affected by: Cross Site Scripting (XSS). The impact is: Allows an attacker to execute arbitrary HTML and JavaScript code via a "redirect" parameter. The component is: Web login form: login.php, lines 40 and 54. The attack vector is: reflected XSS, victim may click the malicious url.
